  09 Feb 2012; Pacho Ramos <pacho@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Drop maintainer due retirement, bug #85926

  03 Dec 2010; Diego E. Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> adtool-1.3.2.ebuild:
  Do a full-rebuild of autotools rather than sticking to automake, so that it
  works with the latest versions. Drop default src_compile.

*adtool-1.3.2 (03 Aug 2009)

  03 Aug 2009; Tobias Scherbaum <dertobi123@gentoo.org>
  -adtool-1.3-r1.ebuild, +adtool-1.3.2.ebuild:
  Version bump, #279526

  11 May 2009; Tobias Scherbaum <dertobi123@gentoo.org>
  adtool-1.3-r1.ebuild:
  Add ~amd64, #269437

  29 Oct 2008; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> adtool-1.3-r1.ebuild:
  Run automake or the asneeded patch will cause maintainer-mode rebuilds
  (which caused further problems here).

  06 Apr 2008; Tobias Scherbaum <dertobi123@gentoo.org>
  adtool-1.3-r1.ebuild:
  want automake 1.7, reported by Mike Auty in #216454

  21 Oct 2006; Tobias Scherbaum <dertobi123@gentoo.org>
  -adtool-1.2-r1.ebuild, -adtool-1.3.ebuild, adtool-1.3-r1.ebuild:
  ppc stable, housekeeping

  01 Aug 2006; Tobias Scherbaum <dertobi123@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  satya's leaving, add myself as maintainer

  31 Jul 2006; Christian Andreetta <satya@gentoo.org> adtool-1.2-r1.ebuild,
  adtool-1.3.ebuild, adtool-1.3-r1.ebuild:
  website changed: from c128.org to gp2x.org

  04 Apr 2006; Christian Andreetta <satya@gentoo.org> -adtool-1.2.ebuild:
  old ebuild cleanup

